name: INFINITY SEED
description: Unleash a universe of visual splendor with INFINITY SEED, where each stroke and hue is a response to your input. In this interactive art series, your chosen seed—a number or a phrase—blooms into a digital tapestry of algorithmic beauty. Every creation is a singular event, a personal dialogue between you and the canvas of possibility. Curate your visual experience and watch as the algorithm weaves your unique narrative into a masterpiece of colors and forms.
